{"tid":735223,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"小米 將於2018年7月20日加入恆指","createTime":"2018-07-09T10:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T22:47:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd163d823522d3142999e7ca5baf0ede737b2126","tid":735223,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"2018 年 7 月 9 日<br />\r指數通告<br />\r恒生指數系列成份股變動<br />\r由於小米集團 - W (<a href=\"http://1810.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1810.HK&d=GVdTxnMf1sKUCcaeuRDk4KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9a959dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1810.HK</a>)符合恒生綜合指數的快速納入指數規則要求，相關指數的 成份股將於2018年7月20日 (星期五) 收市後有下列變動，並於2018年7月23日 (星期一) 起生效。<br />\r    公司名稱<br />\r   <br />\r將被納入下列指數及其分類指數<br />\r <br />\r  小米集團 -W (<a href=\"http://1810.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1810.HK&d=GVdTxnMf1sKUCcaeuRDk4KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9a959dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1810.HK</a>)<br />\r 恒生綜合指數<br />\no 恒生綜合行業指數 &ndash; 資訊科技業 o 恒生綜合大型股指數<br />\no 恒生綜合大中型股指數<br />\r 恒生環球綜合指數<br />\n 恒生互聯網科技業指數<br />\r 如有查詢，請電郵至:info@hsi.com.hk。 #完#<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hsi.com.hk/static/uploads/contents/zh_hk/news/indexChgNotice/20180709T161600.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsi.com.hk%2Fstatic%2Fuploads%2Fcontents%2Fzh_hk%2Fnews%2FindexChgNotice%2F20180709T161600.pdf&d=GVdTxnMf1sKUCcaeuRDk4KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=82158edb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hsi.com.hk/static/uploads/contents/zh_hk/news/indexChgNotice/20180709T161600.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"d0fb3a873d22e30ce0995e81f459b15c7cfdc703","tid":735223,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"下，點解可以入恆指？"},{"pid":"1fc0cad0b28faf93dbecf0e83dec225fe891a4fd","tid":735223,"uid":9900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0fb3a873d22e30ce0995e81f459b15c7cfdc703","tid":735223,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score